   },
   {
      "type":"richtext",
      "id":"page_returns_privacy_policy_step_7",
      "label":"Copy 7",
      "default":"<p>We Will Send No Other Emails Unless You Ask Us To Do So.<\/p>"
   },
   {
      "type":"header",
      "content":"Terms of Service"
   },
    {
      "type":"textarea",
      "id":"page_returns_terms_header",
      "label":"Header",
      "default":"Terms of Sale"
   },
   {
      "type":"header",
      "content":"Column 1"
   },
   {
      "type":"text",
      "id":"page_returns_terms_header_1",
      "label":"Header",
      "default":"Payment Terms"
   },
   {
      "type":"textarea",
      "id":"page_returns_terms_column_1",
      "label":"Copy",
      "default":"<p>Your Credit Card Information Will Be Validated When You Complete The Website Checkout Process. Typically Website Orders Are Shipped And Billed Within One Business Day Of Receipt.<\/p>"
   },
   {
      "type":"header",
      "content":"Column 2"
   },
   {
      "type":"text",
      "id":"page_returns_terms_header_2",
      "label":"Header",
      "default":"Freight Policy"
   },
   {
      "type":"textarea",
      "id":"page_returns_terms_column_2",
      "label":"Copy",
      "default":"<p>Shipments Are Made From Our Facility Near Tampa, Florida. You Are Responsible For Paying Freight Charges From Our Facility To Your Location Via The Carrier Of Our Choice. Freight Charges Are Shown During Order Processing. We Do Not Ship To Locations Outside The Continental United States.<\/p>"
   },
   {
      "type":"header",
      "content":"Column 3"
   },
   {
      "type":"text",
      "id":"page_returns_terms_header_3",
      "label":"Header",
      "default":"Freight Damage \/ Incorrect Shipments"
   },
   {
      "type":"textarea",
      "id":"page_returns_terms_column_3",
      "label":"Copy",
      "default":"<p>Claims For Damaged, Missing, Or Incorrect Shipments Must Be Made Within 48 Hours Following Carrier Delivery Of Your Shipment.  Please Inspect Your Shipment Immediately And Notify Us Of Problems: Phone (800) 942-7639 Email <a class='text-primary' href='mailto:info@harneyhardware.com'>info@harneyhardware.com<\/a>.<\/p>"
